description:
Marie is a fighter who sells her skills to the highest bidder. With her friend and blood brother, William, she fights the 'Dragons' – strange creatures that hover on the borderline of reality.

Along with her sister Armance, Marie is in search of Georges d'Aiscelin, one of the murderers responsible for the massacre of their family, fifteen years earlier. Having lost his trail and needing money, they accept an apparently simple mission; to escort a monk and a treasure of the French church safely out of the kingdom of Milan...

But soon, on the road through the Alps, the pursuit becomes a deadly struggle. Furthermore, the shade of the cruel Georges d'Aiscelin, and Lou, the young brother of Marie, overshadows their path.
name: Revenge 2/2

description: What's worse than being trapped within Rocket's pocket-dimension vial? Realizing you're not alone! What strange creature stalks the GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY?

volume.name: Marvel Universe Guardians of the Galaxy Infinite Comic

description:
THE MEGA-EPIC, MEGA-MOMENTOUS LAST ISSUE OF MEGA MAN BEFORE HIATUS IS HERE! "Everlasting Peace": When an experiment at the Chronos Institute goes awry, Dr. Light is sent on a journey through time and space! Join us as we follow Mega Man across the ages and learn what it really means to be "Mega Man"! What legacy will the Blue Bomber leave and what will Dr. Light gain from this epic journey? Find out as we take a historic glimpse into the legendary adventures of Mega Man featuring the worlds of Mega Man, Mega Man X and even further beyond for the FIRST TIME EVER with the worlds of Mega Man Zero, Mega Man ZX and Mega Man Legends!

description:
Mayhem, murder, and bloodshed, the only way Veronica believes she can get to the top. Leading Moon Streak on his first villainous outing proves to be more complicated than she ever dreams and instead of skyrocketing to infamy V and Moon Streak head home with some furry new friends.

Note: The digital edition (12/2/2015) for this issue was released before the print edition.

While the United States are accused of wanting to found a New World Order, disasters continue to go on all around the world, and the secret Apollo XX mission lands on the moon where they make a major discovery...
name: Exogenesis 1/2

description: It's a kettle-full of high-climbing rescue as Dr Pierre and co. attempt to get to the missing baby from the shadowy mastermind, who remains...in the shadows!

The young investigator, Sofia d'Agostino, and her bodyguard Angelo Costanza, a former killer for the Mafia, are confronted with a Commando squad connected to an occult branch of the Vatican. Without knowing it, they are taking part in a thousand-year-old fight for the protection of the Faith...

After the lively reception at the monastery at Mount Athos, Sofia and Gina try to save Angelo and Father Dimitrios. Unfortunately, the enemy is waiting for them...
name: Die and Let Live 1/2

description: CJ has discovered that her daughter Sunflower is alive after ten years of believing a man named Rush Bridge had killed her. She has followed what clues she has to an Officer Leshing, whom she believes can help her find her daughter... Will CJ finally be able to rescue her abducted child and enact revenge upon the man who has taken the last ten years from her or will the mysterious man named Rush kill Sunflower's mother as he did her father?
Beast Boy does too. many. chores. at Titans Tower, so he joins his buddy Aqualad for the easy life under the sea. But making his lazy-living dreams come true isn't nearly as simple as he imagines!
name: Sea Changes

description:
What would have happened if the Dallas attack had taken place in 1973?

Washington D.C., 1965. The re-elected President has decided to begin his second term with a decisive ground offensive into Communist North Vietnam. At the same time, protest actions in the USA are increasing, against both the war and the emerging dictatorial military junta...
name: Who Killed the President? 1/2

description:
With influences ranging from 19th century atrocity prints to the Sex Pistols, and obsessions with horror, scatology and human freaks, Maruo has taken the "erotic-grotesque" (ero-guro) style of manga, a unique fusion of sex and violence to its ultimate extreme.

Ultra-Gash Inferno is the ultimate compendium of Suehiro Maruo's most shocking and graphically precise work, containing nine psycho-nightmares never before translated and published in English. With a translation by James Havoc (author of Butchershop In The Sky) and Takako Shinkado, and an introduction by Romain Slocombe, Ultra-Gash Inferno is a revelatory cross-cultural event in comic-book publishing.
name: TPB

description: A new invention of Barabas can connect computers directly to the human brain via bluetooth. A mighty industrialist wants Barabas' invention and lets Snoeffel and Gaffel download Barabas' brain on a usb stick. Barabas is left behind as a helpless infant. Meanwhile, Lambik connects his "superior intellect" to the internet and thus everything goes wrong: world peace is threatened! Can Suske and Wiske get Barabas back to normal and prevent a new world war?
name: Het Verloren Verleden
Zizi und peter Panpan: Es lebe die sexuelle Revolution!
